<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<div type="elementDocumentation" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="contentLocation">
    <head>
        
        <!-- PREMIS Semantic unit 1.7.1.0 -->
        <abbr>1.7.1</abbr>
        <gi>contentLocation</gi>
        
    </head>
    
    <div type="semanticcomponents">
        <!-- PREMIS Semantic components -->
        <p>1.7.1.1 contentLocationType</p>
        <p>1.7.1.2 contentLocationValue</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="definition">
        <!-- PREMIS Definition -->
        <p>Information needed to retrieve a physical item from its physical storage
            location or a file from the storage system, or to access a bitstream
            within a file.</p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- PREMIS Rationale -->
    
    <div type="usagenotes">
        <!-- PREMIS Usage notes -->
        <p>If the preservation repository uses the <bold>objectIdentifier</bold> as a
            handle for retrieving data, <bold>contentLocation</bold> is implicit and
            does not need to be recorded.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="datatype">
        <!-- PREMIS Data constraint -->
        <p>Container</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="entity">
        <!-- PREMIS Object category -->
        <p>
            <table cols="5">
                <row role="label">
                    <cell> </cell>
                    <cell><bold>Intellectual Entity</bold></cell>
                    <cell><bold>Representation</bold></cell>
                    <cell><bold>File</bold></cell>
                    <cell><bold>Bitstream</bold></cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><bold>Applicability</bold></cell>
                    <cell>Not applicable</cell>
                    <cell>Applicable</cell>
                    <cell>Applicable</cell>
                    <cell>Applicable</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><bold>Repeatability</bold></cell>
                    <cell> </cell>
                    <cell>Not repeatable</cell>
                    <cell>Not repeatable</cell>
                    <cell>Not repeatable</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><bold>Obligation</bold></cell>
                    <cell> </cell>
                    <cell>Optional</cell>
                    <cell>Optional</cell>
                    <cell>Optional</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div type="creationmaintenance">
        <!-- PREMIS Creation / Maintenance -->
        <p>A preservation repository will normally refer to content that it
            controls. Therefore, it is assumed that the repository will normally
            assign the <bold>contentLocation</bold>, probably by a program.</p>
    </div>
</div>

